      "name": "How much notice must a Texas school give before an ARD meeting?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Texas law requires the district to provide written notice at least 5 calendar days before an ARD meeting. Parents can waive this notice in writing if they choose to meet sooner."
      }
